name: Prachi
greetingText: Meri surat bhulati, Tere naa de akhar ne
wishText: Kol Tere Mainu Aan De Soniyo Kara Main Kitne Jatan Oh Soniyo Duron Dooron Main Vekhan Tenu Soniyo Kahaan Tu Kahaan Main Kehnde Zehr Vekh Ke Peeta Te Ki Peeta Ishq Soch Ke Kita Te Ki Kita Dil De Ke Dil Lainde Aas Rakhi Ve Bulleya Pyaar Vi Laalach Naal Kita Te Ki Kita‚Äù
